metadata.name: Nieux Brieux #1
metadata.description:
Original artwork created for The Nieux Society by New Orleans artist JP Gebbia.

The Nieux Brieux NFT allows you to enjoy one free Nieux Brieux beer any time you visit NOLA Brewing Company in New Orleans. Each Nieux Brieux is masterfully brewed by the Director of Funk Derek Lintern with a goal to inspire you to dream, explore and try new things to foster a Golden Age of Creativity in New Orleans.
